Fireplace (gas and wood) in living room and family room.   Basement is plumbed for a 3rd bathroom and has Daylight windows. Extensive decking, patio and shed to store your lake toys.  Enjoy the beautiful sunsets in your own backyard over looking the lake.  Come see why lake living is everyones dream.
